title: Duke Nukem Zero Hour playthrough -- Part 2
description: Since I lost my save file I had to playthrough the beginning again. I changed the settings to high resolution textures, which ended up lowering the framerate quite a bit. This game was really fun and cool, and I'm glad to have finally played it! Thanks Pogokeen! I'm thinking of playing it again on Hard, finding all the time machine parts, in first person and with low res textures to raise FPS as much as possible.
